definitions.definition: A native or resident of the state of Michigan in the United States of America .
In particular, a man from Michigan , contrasted with a Michigoose ( “ woman from Michigan ” ) .

main_definition: ( US ) A native or resident of the state of Michigan in the United States of America .
secondary_definitions: ( uncommon , humorous ) In particular, a man from Michigan , contrasted with a Michigoose ( “ woman from Michigan ” ) .
